Installation requirements:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

OCAML 3.12.1
OCAMLFIND (FINDLIB)

GMP 5.0.1
MPFR 3.0.0

CAMLLIB_accstrat (revision 850)
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/bjeannet/pkg/camllib/branches/accstrat

FIXPOINT_accstrat (revision 850)
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/bjeannet/pkg/camllib/branches/accstrat

MLGMPIDL (revision 191)
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/mlxxxidl/mlgmpidl/trunk

APRON  (revision 1013) 
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svnroot/apron/apron/trunk

MLCUDDIDL (includes CUDD 2.4.2) (revision 271) 
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/mlxxxidl/mlcuddidl/trunk

BDDAPRON (revision 942)
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/bjeannet/pkg/bddapron/trunk

-----------------------------
with max-strategy iteration:
-----------------------------

YICES 1.0.28
  http://yices.csl.sri.com/download.shtml

OCAMLYICES 0.3
  https://github.com/polazarus/ocamlyices

EGLIB 2.6.7
  http://www.dii.uchile.cl/~daespino/EGlib_doc/main.html

QSOPT_EX 2.5.6
  http://www.dii.uchile.cl/~daespino/ESolver_doc/main.html

STRATIMP 0.3.1
  provided on the ReaVer web page

